openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: Spec with a simple validated argument for extensibility testing
  version: 1
paths:
  /test-validation:
    get:
      tags:
        - search
      summary: >-
        Used to test validation
      operationId: TestValidation
      parameters:
        - name: maxLengthRestrictedTo8String
          schema:
            type: string
            maxLength: 8
          in: query
          required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: object is valid
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
        '400':
          description: object is invalid
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
